<p><strong>What we do about allegations of harassment:</strong></p>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: GIF captioned "Sherlock Homeboy" — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>
<ul>
  <li>Looking into all similar claims about an accused individual to see if the problem has become systematic.</li>
  <li>Keeping an eye on data from the company — making sure we are avoiding discriminatory behaviors (such as hiring/firing employees of a certain race/gender/religion by a manager).</li>
  <li>Conduct private and discrete interviews to gather information about the situation/individual accused.</li>
</ul>', 9, TRUE, 3
