INSERT INTO learn_lessons (module_id, title, slug, content, display_order, is_published, estimated_minutes)
SELECT m.id, 'Why We Have Company Policies', 'why-we-have-company-policies', '<h2>Why We Have Company Policies</h2>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: "What''s the Policy Again?" graphic — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>
<p>So, why do we have company policies? Well, think of it as our secret sauce for making things run smoothly here at Innovative Air Technologies. It''s all about setting up clear rules and guidelines so everyone knows what''s what — from who does what, to how we all should behave. It''s like having a roadmap for work, making sure we''re all heading in the same direction and staying on track.</p>
<p>Now, we all know the business world doesn''t stand still, right? It''s always changing, and so are we. That''s why we update our policies regularly, tweaking them to stay in line with the latest industry standards, legal stuff, and what we need to keep our operations humming. And we''ll be sure to keep you in the loop with any changes because <strong>we''re all in this together.</strong></p>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: "We''re All In This Together" graphic — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>
<p>Here at Innovative Air Technologies, putting our people first is what we''re all about. We believe in setting up policies that are not just rules for the sake of rules, but ones that actually support and respect everyone. It''s our way of making sure this place isn''t just a workplace, but a community where everyone feels valued, protected, and part of something bigger. Pretty cool, right?</p>
<h3>And let''s talk about talking...</h3>
<p>It''s a big deal for us. Keeping the lines of communication wide open between the management team and you guys is key.</p>
<p>Got a question?</p>
<p>A concern?</p>
<p>A suggestion?</p>
<p><strong>We''re all ears.</strong></p>
<p>We like to keep things open and honest to help us build a place where trust isn''t just a word, but how we roll. Together, we''re all about making Innovative Air Technologies not just a great place to work, but a place where work feels great.</p>', 0, TRUE, 2
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
WHERE c.slug = 'company' AND m.slug = 'company-policies'
ON CONFLICT (module_id, slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO learn_lessons (module_id, title, slug, content, display_order, is_published, estimated_minutes)
SELECT m.id, 'Company Policy Manual', 'company-policy-manual', '<h2>Company Policy Manual</h2>
<p>As a new member of the Innovative Air Technologies team, it is important that you download and review our company policy manual. This manual contains important information that we cover in this training course about our company''s policies and procedures, as well as guidelines for conduct in the workplace. It is essential that you familiarize yourself with this document to ensure that you are aware of our expectations and standards.</p>
<p>Once you have downloaded the company policy manual, please retain it for your records. This document serves as a valuable resource for you to refer back to whenever needed. If you have any questions or require clarification on any of the policies outlined in the manual, please do not hesitate to reach out to us. We are always available to answer any questions you may have and provide guidance as needed.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.dehumidifiers.com">IAT_Company_Policy_Manual_rev8.2025.pdf</a></p>', 1, TRUE, 2
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
WHERE c.slug = 'company' AND m.slug = 'company-policies'
ON CONFLICT (module_id, slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO learn_lessons (module_id, title, slug, content, display_order, is_published, estimated_minutes)
SELECT m.id, 'Professional Conduct Matters', 'professional-conduct-matters', '<h2>Professional Conduct Matters</h2>
<blockquote><p><em>Our company values everyone getting along, acting professionally, and just being all-around decent to each other.</em></p></blockquote>
<p>It''s all about making sure we''ve got a cool, safe, and super productive place to work. Be kind, polite, and considerate of how others are feeling and what they need. Plus, working well together, whether it''s with your teammates or the bosses, is a big deal around here.</p>
<p>Just a heads up, though — if someone''s not playing by these rules and gets a bit out of line, there might be some consequences.</p>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: "That one might have an after effect" meme — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>', 2, TRUE, 2
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
WHERE c.slug = 'company' AND m.slug = 'company-policies'
ON CONFLICT (module_id, slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO learn_lessons (module_id, title, slug, content, display_order, is_published, estimated_minutes)
SELECT m.id, 'Why We Have a Dress Code', 'why-we-have-a-dress-code', '<h2>Why We Have a Dress Code</h2>
<p>At Innovative Air Technologies, we''re all about creating a culture that''s professional, respectful, and, most importantly, safe.</p>
<p>When everyone brings their A-game, dressed for success and treating each other right, it sets the tone for the whole place. It''s about showing our best selves to our customers, partners, and each other.</p>
<p>So, we''ve put together this little guide to help everyone understand what''s expected when it comes to how we act and dress around here.</p>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Employee in IAT-branded clothing — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>', 3, TRUE, 2
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
WHERE c.slug = 'company' AND m.slug = 'company-policies'
ON CONFLICT (module_id, slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO learn_lessons (module_id, title, slug, content, display_order, is_published, estimated_minutes)
SELECT m.id, 'Dress Code: General Guidelines', 'dress-code-general-guidelines', '<h2>Dress Code: General Guidelines</h2>
<p>At Innovative Air Technologies (IAT), we believe that an employee''s personal appearance and hygiene reflect the company''s character and professionalism. Our dress code is designed to ensure that employees are comfortable, safe, and appropriately represent the company while performing their duties.</p>
<ul>
<li>Employees are expected to dress appropriately based on their individual work responsibilities and positions.</li>
<li>Professional attire is required during external meetings, with IAT company shirts or designated attire for customer or vendor visits, ensuring a consistent and professional image.</li>
<li>Clothing should be clean, well-maintained, and free from rips, tears, or offensive logos or slogans.</li>
<li>Personal hygiene should be maintained to a high standard.</li>
</ul>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Dress Code General Guidelines video thumbnail — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>', 4, TRUE, 3
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
WHERE c.slug = 'company' AND m.slug = 'company-policies'
ON CONFLICT (module_id, slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO learn_lessons (module_id, title, slug, content, display_order, is_published, estimated_minutes)
SELECT m.id, 'Dress Code: Prohibited Attire', 'dress-code-prohibited-attire', '<h2>Dress Code: Prohibited Attire</h2>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: "How ''Bout No" meme graphic — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>
<h3>So, here''s the deal:</h3>
<ul>
<li>First off, let''s keep it classy and respectful with our outfits. That means no clothes with rude words, pictures, or catchphrases. We''re all about good vibes here.</li>
<li>Next, we love to be comfy, but let''s save the super casual stuff like sweatpants, flip-flops, or tank tops for the weekends, unless your manager says it''s cool.</li>
<li>And lastly, let''s aim for clothes that aren''t too revealing or super tight. We''re all for expressing yourself, but let''s keep it professional.</li>
</ul>
<blockquote><p><strong>Thanks for keeping the workplace awesome for everyone!</strong></p></blockquote>', 5, TRUE, 2
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
WHERE c.slug = 'company' AND m.slug = 'company-policies'
ON CONFLICT (module_id, slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO learn_lessons (module_id, title, slug, content, display_order, is_published, estimated_minutes)
SELECT m.id, 'Personnel Files', 'personnel-files', '<h2>Personnel Files</h2>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Understanding Your Personnel File video thumbnail — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>
<blockquote><p><em>Our policy is established to ensure transparency, privacy, and security in the handling of employee records.</em></p></blockquote>
<p>We recognize that personnel files contain sensitive and confidential information, ranging from employment history to performance evaluations. This policy is in place to strike a balance between employee rights to access their own information and the need to safeguard this data against unauthorized access.</p>
<p>Having this policy allows employees to review and understand the information kept in their files, fostering an environment of trust and open communication. It also ensures that our company adheres to legal standards regarding data privacy and employee rights. By regulating access to personnel files, we protect the integrity of employee data, maintain confidentiality, and uphold our commitment to ethical and responsible information management. This policy is a key part of our dedication to creating a respectful, secure, and transparent workplace for all our employees.</p>', 6, TRUE, 3
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
WHERE c.slug = 'company' AND m.slug = 'company-policies'
ON CONFLICT (module_id, slug) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO learn_lessons (module_id, title, slug, content, display_order, is_published, estimated_minutes)
SELECT m.id, 'Access to Personnel Records', 'access-to-personnel-records', '<h2>Access to Personnel Records</h2>
<p>So, here''s the deal: The company has a file for each and every one of us, kind of like our own little dossier. They try to keep it under wraps as much as they can.</p>
<figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: "It''s classified" meme — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>
<p>If you''re curious about what''s in your file, you can totally ask to see it. Just say the word!</p>
<p>Now, it''s super important that this file has got all the right info about you. If anything changes — like your name, where you live, your phone number, who to call in an emergency, or even your marital status — you''ve gotta let the company know.</p>
<p>Oh, and if by chance you forget to update your info and it ends up costing you, just remember, the company''s not picking up the tab for that. That''s on you, buddy.</p>', 7, TRUE, 2
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
